messages.messageBody:
Below are dates for homeschool and family camps at
DeBenneville Pines in California. Look at the web
site www.debenneville.org for details, and also for
other adult offerings, like men's and women's
retreats.


Spring Homeschool Camp 4/19 � 4/22/04

Rainbow Family Camp 3/26 � 3/28/04

Fall Homeschool Camp 9/27 � 9/30/04


For additional information on any of these events,

Contact the camp office at (909) 794-2928 phone
(909) 794-2418 fax uucamp@...
e-mail
de Benneville website www.uucamp.org

I haven't attended any of these camps...yet. But they
sound good :) We'll be at the Rethinking Education
conference in Dallas in May.

heather m
tucson az
